{"tid":723062,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"梨狀肌(可能)傷咗可唔可以行遠路?","createTime":"2018-06-30T05:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T20:37:11.000Z","uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96a81977b4673849f709e0a9a83e676b629cb741","tid":723062,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"前日練腳，做咗squats, leg raises, side leg raises。<br />\n尋日右腳痛，行都唔係行得好流暢同舒服，痛位就大致上係下圖果2個<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></strong>點位，姐係右股前後。<br />\n尋日半夜都好咗D嫁喇。<br />\n上網search過好似係梨狀肌傷左。<br />\n不過慣咗隔日跑步，唔落吓街個心唔係好舒服，所以想問下如果真係梨狀肌傷，噤可唔可以落街行下，例如2個鐘? 再行奈D又可唔可以?<br />\n唔該先!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/135359_d5adb6ad5c3245a3b68afd113b8c326f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F135359_d5adb6ad5c3245a3b68afd113b8c326f.jpg&h=cd73ea55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"421971a8d64bf98ee373c4d82d4aa3486ed7dd6a","tid":723062,"uid":84282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:20:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a36e21f9fb88bc2a2fffa46bc18391ba9e9af02","tid":723062,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T20:37:11.000Z","msg":"推推"}]}